desc: Quirky place that offers home decor stuffs, accessories for your home, Also conducts workshops in IOD, kitchen stuffs, Christmas decor, Sola Wood flowers, Wood painting, DIY supplies, hardware -knobs, APC paints. Located at Grimshaw, Alberta. Offers local delivery. Shop Online

layout.text: A Hidden Gem in Small Town Grimshaw!!!! Come on in and get inspired to decorate your yard or home this spring!
